@Steve L
I absolutely agree that the new comments reply format is horrible.

I was following a thread yesterday (or maybe the day before?) where I was trying to read the reply to a reply to a reply, etc. I think it was 6 or 7 layers deep, and the last level was squeezed into a column about 4 or 5 letters wide down the right side of my phone screen - very effectively rendering it as unreadable gibberish.

